nft_description:
Avatar representing Believer #5539, a Devotee of Hisato.

    // READ ME - Important Notice about variable Attributes //
    
    [Equipped]
    Purchasing a Spirit Key Avatar does *NOT* grant you any of the accompanying “Equipped” attributes.
    Attributes marked “Equipped”, and their underlying Relic NFT are *NOT* transferred or sold together with a Spirit Key Avatar.
    The attribute is removed when either the underlying Relic NFT or underlying Spirit Key Avatar is transferred or sold.
    
    [Customizable]
    Attributes marked “Customizable” can be changed by the holder.
    
    [Fixed]
    Attributes marked “Fixed” cannot be changed by the holder, and are randomly assigned at reveal.
5000 little jerks polluting the Ethereum blockchain. They may be cute but they're totally unbearable. Don't try to adopt one, you'll thank me later.

This photo captures a moment of breathtaking beauty, but it also speaks to something deeper and more profound. They are made up of several handmade layers, each taken from a 1/1 in the collection. The I'M NEW HERE film is a documentary about Cryptoart, its history, and the community of artists, visionaries, and builders that has formed around it. It features an incredible cast of people that have made this space their home. Full list here: https://www.newhere.xyz/cast
